node.text: We were asked by the BBC to collaborate with them to highlight some of the dangers in the trading world. We are proud to have engaged with this production and hopefully people can be cautious when entering the market. It’s on BBC iPlayer for those to enjoy, I’ll be uploading it on my YouTube soon also 🚀

node.text:
And here we GO! Astrofx Dubai Trading Floor! The journey is officially underway! 
After all the mayhem this past year we have continued to grow Astrofx globally. We are continuing to recruit the best trading talent across the world, providing them with our capital to trade on a institution level. 

Astrofx have decided to push the industry further once again, so for all Astrofx funded traders from anywhere in the world -
when you show us consistency for 3+ months we will be covering your accommodation costs whilst you visit out trading floor in Dubai.

Similar to our trading floor in Mayfair, London. Once you join Astrofx we make our trading floor free to use for anybody who wants to take their trading to the next level. 

Who wants in? Contact us via my bio and get more details. 📹 @yliforreal

node.title: The Dubai Trading floor journey begins!

node.text:
Video of another 22 people recruited at Astrofx who are now trading with the fund.
This brings the total up to 200+ worldwide active traders managing our capital, I decided to give them an induction personally and welcome them onboard.
If your willing to work, if your willing to spend countless hours towards your craft and think you have what it takes, then contact me using the link in my bio or just feel free to DM me. Can’t wait to do these inductions face to face soon! #Astrofx

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Aman Natt in Mayfair, W1 London. May be an image of 1 person, indoor and office.

node.text:
The Astrofx HQ busier than ever! Here is just some of our Astrofx funded traders at work today. 
Our floor is open to all our students on any-day they want to come in! 
From learning the foundations of the markets, to in depth daily breakdowns and just overall being around like minded traders with similar ambitions! 
If you see yourself wanting to come and see what it’s like in our offices, shoot a message to the link in my bio! #Astrofx #Traders #Mayfair #London
